Fluxus : (C) 2005 Dave Griffiths : dave at pawfal dot org : www.pawfal.org

fluxus is a dependancy heavy application

requires:
ode        http://opende.sourceforge.net/
guile      http://www.gnu.org/software/guile/guile.html
fftw       http://www.fftw.org/
portaudio  http://www.portaudio.com/
libsndfile http://www.mega-nerd.com/libsndfile/
liblo      http://plugin.org.uk/liblo/

and if that's not enough, you'll also need scons (http://www.scons.org/) to build fluxus

to build, type:

scons
scons install (as root)



